Package: StreamNetgstat
Type: Package
Title: Spatial stream networks analysis
Version: 1.0.0
Authors@R: c(person("Valeria", "Callioni", role = c("aut", "cre"),
	email = "valeria.callioni@mail.polimi.it"))
Description: This package provides a C++ implementation of functions that allow the user to fit a spatial
						 linear model on a stream network, with the final goal to perform kriging. The data it can
						 handle are the .ssn directories provided by the SSN package. 
Depends: R (>= 3.2.0), Rcpp (>= 0.12.16), RcppEigen (>= 0.3.3.4.0), SSN, rlist
LinkingTo: Rcpp, RcppEigen
NeedsCompilation: yes
SystemRequirements: C++11
License: What license is it under?
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
RoxygenNote: 6.1.1
